ITEM NO.15               COURT NO.12               SECTION XIV
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CIVIL) Diary No(s). 18983/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  20-02-2024
in FAO (COMM) No. 36/2024 passed by the High Court of Delhi at New 
Delhi]
UNION OF INDIA                                     Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
M/S GITWAKO FARMS PRIVATE LIMITED                  Respondent(s)
FOR ADMISSION and I.R. 
IA No. 120579/2025 - CONDONATION OF DELAY IN FILING
 
Date : 04-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE PAMIDIGHANTAM SRI NARASIMHA
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE R. MAHADEVAN
         (PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) :Mr. Satya Darshi Sanjay, A.S.G.
                   Mr. Mukesh Kumar Maroria, AOR
                   Mr. Akshay Amritanshu, Adv.
                   Mr. Aaditya Shankar Dixit, Adv.
                   Mr. Shantnu Sharma, Adv.
                   Mr. Jagdish Chandra, Adv.
                   Mr. Rajeshwari Shankar, Adv.                   
                   
For Respondent(s) : 
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
1.Delay condoned.
2.Learned  counsel  for  the  petitioner  submits  that  similar
matters have already been dismissed.  In view of the statement,
this special leave petition also stands dismissed.
3.Pending application(s), if any, shall stand disposed of.
(INDU MARWAH)                                   (NIDHI WASON)
 AR-cum-PS                                   COURT MASTER (NSH)
